Trader Stan's Trading Post is a unique series of shops, operated by the Trader crewmembers and Trader Stan. There is a separate shop instance at each of the charter ship locations.

Each shop has an identical inventory which includes the standard general store, however the prices are twice as expensive compared to regular general stores. The Trading Post also carries exotic items in addition to the general store stock.

The shop closest to a bank is the one in Port Khazard.
